All-cause and disease-specific mortality among male, former elite athletes: an 
average 50-year follow-up.

Kettunen JA(1), Kujala UM(2), Kaprio J(3), Bäckmand H(4), Peltonen M(5), 
Eriksson JG(6), Sarna S(7).

Author information:
(1)Arcada University of Applied Sciences, Helsinki, Finland.
(2)Department of Health Sciences, University of Jyväskylä, Jyväskylä, Finland.
(3)Department of Public Health, University of Helsinki, Hjelt Institute, 
Helsinki, Finland Department of Mental Health and Substance Abuse Services, 
