Adrenal insufficiency: review of clinical outcomes with current glucocorticoid 
replacement therapy.

Johannsson G(1), Falorni A, Skrtic S, Lennernäs H, Quinkler M, Monson JP, 
Stewart PM.

Author information:
(1)Department of Endocrinology, Sahlgrenska Academy, University of Gothenburg, 
